00:00:31.694 --> 00:00:42.290
Of the Riemann integral, which,
remember, from the discussion

00:00:42.290 --> 00:00:44.150
at the end of the
last lecture, is

00:00:44.150 --> 00:00:49.345
a theory of area underneath
