00:52:08.630 --> 00:52:10.940
which are becoming
finer and finer-- so

00:52:10.940 --> 00:52:12.560
with the norm converging to 0.

00:52:21.780 --> 00:52:26.190
Then I want to show
that limit as r

00:52:26.190 --> 00:52:29.670
