of the Riemann sums

00:52:29.670 --> 00:52:35.010
corresponding to this
sequence of partial sums--

00:52:35.010 --> 00:52:38.850
[INAUDIBLE] partial sums--
this sequence of partitions

00:52:38.850 --> 00:52:42.270
exists, and equals
this number I,

00:52:42.270 --> 00:52:47.840
which I obtained from this
